etomica.models.nitrogen

Class FindPairMoleculeIndexBetaN2

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.models.nitrogen.FindPairMoleculeIndexBetaN2

  • public class FindPairMoleculeIndexBetaN2
extends java.lang.Object
    BETA-NITROGEN MODEL Class to identify the pair of molecules that are the same in terms of displacement vector and orientation This is done to speed up the construction of the Hessian Matrix such that we do not have to recalculate the block matrix that is the same. The index field is a 5-dimensional array index[0] is x-direction displacement index[1] is y-direction displacement index[2] is z-direction displacement index[3] is the orientation of moleculeA index[4] is the orientation of moleculeB The isNewPair array is to keep track whether the pair with index[][][][][] has been looped over or not.
